class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
News Website Examples - 5 Sites That Inform and Inspire</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">This just in: these 5 news website examples spotlight real-time stories and events with visually engaging content and easy site navigation.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
class="card-byline-image">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/cl-20240522_2024-06-03-112510_nwiw.jpg?crop=1:1,smart&width=80&dpr=2"
width="80"
height="80"
alt="Carla Lottering"
/></div><div
class="card-byline-details">
<span>By <a
class="card-byline-author" href="https://www.zarla.com/contributors/carla-lottering">Carla Lottering</a>,</span>
<span
class="card-byline-date">Jul 26, 2024</span><div
class="card-byline-bio">
Carla is a Copywriter for Zarla based in Cape Town, South Africa. She has over 5 years&#039; experience in online content creation and writes extensively on logos for small businesses.</div></div></div></div><div
class="card-image-holder"><div
class="card-preview">
