src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>I value the desktop site's ample use of white space as it ensures all content appears organized and concise, contributing to a seamless browsing experience. However, I think the search bar should be added to the top menu bar for more prominence.</p><p>I found all pages and images to load quite quickly, which is also indicated by its optimal performance score of 94/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test. However, the test also noted that the site's accessibility practices could be improved upon.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-the-narwhal-824x16382-20240723.webp"
