</span>
<span>Dublin, Ireland</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Rugby365 is a news platform aggregating rugby-related news from both local and international teams, offering up-to-date match scores, results, video interviews, and fixtures. The website's bright color palette grabbed my attention and its strategic use across several pages helped me focus in on various CTA buttons.</p><p>While I feel like some aesthetic tweaks, such as the inclusion of more high-quality images, could be made to improve the website's overall appeal, I do like the addition of recent match scores at the top of the home page as it's a great drawing card for rugby enthusiasts.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
