</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>I enjoyed having access to a wide variety of articles covering many rugby topics, such as upcoming tournaments, country-specific team news, and a section on sports rules and regulations. The inclusion of video content adds visual interest to the website.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>According to WAVE, the site has a large number of contrast ratios, particularly between the top menu bar's text and its color background. I also think the company logo could be enlarged at the top of the home page to increase brand recognition.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-rugby365-3840x8867-20240723.webp"
data-type="desktop"
